narratives.question_text: Were the resources available to you - library, fabrication labs, classroom, software, desk space, etc. adequate for the fulfillment of the assigned work?  If not, please make suggestions.
comments: The resources available were more than adequate for the fulfillment of the assigned work.

Yes, the resources made available were adequate. However, the first paper in the course was supposed to be on a place we had lived outside of New Haven, and so finding adequate resources in the Yale library system was difficult.
Yes, the resources are adequate for me to fulfill my paper and other work.
Readings were easily accessed online for this course.
All resources were more than adequate.
